<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1179.101388.figure13>
    dc:description "Figure 13. Cryphalus numidicus A distribution B lateral and dorsal view C aedeagus D SEM, specimen from Leonidio, Greece E SEM (43 x magnification), specimen from Leonidio, Greece." ;
